# Vercel build context exclusions.
#
# Owner: Aether-Vercel (NP T6 deploy lane).
#
# Aether-Vercel resume-4 update: AI-asset bundle migrated off-Lambda to
# Vercel Blob (region iad1, 1 GB free tier). The 96 active assets are
# uploaded via `npm run upload-assets` (scripts/upload-assets-to-blob.ts)
# and resolved at runtime through `public/asset_manifest.json`. The
# `_Reference/` source tree is no longer needed in the deploy upload at
# all; this exclusion drops the upload from ~650 MB raw + ~370 MB
# resolved (resume-2 state) to a thin Lambda well under the 500 MB
# ephemeral storage limit.
#
# Original V6 D1 decision: active asset bundle was included via
# per-category symlinks under public/assets/ai/. Resume-2 superseded D1
# with local pre-resolve. Resume-4 supersedes resume-2 with the Blob
# migration (build still failed at the Lambda 500 MB ceiling).

.git
node_modules
.next
.venv
__pycache__
tests/
.env
.env.local
_skills_staging/
_meta/
_Reference/
*.test.ts
*.spec.ts
